
# Prerequisites

 * meson
 * ninja

# Configuration

 * Simplest invocation:
 ```
 meson setup builddir
 ```
 * with prefix and options:
 ```
 meson setup --prefix=/opt/libraw -Dopenmp=enabled -Djpeg=enabled -Dzlib=enabled -Dlcms=enabled builddir
 ```
 * without examples
 ```
 meson setup --prefix=/opt/libraw -Dopenmp=enabled -Djpeg=enabled -Dzlib=enabled -Dlcms=enabled -Dexamples=false builddir
 ```
 